        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Public Safety Retirees Healthcare Protection Act</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to increase from $3,000 to $6,000 the amount excludible from the gross income of public safety officers for distributions from governmental retirement plans for health and long-term care insurance. </p> <p><strong></strong></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
